commit 0b72b4970097435f6ae4f7be52bfe4325c495d39
Author: Balazs Scheidler <bazsi@balabit.hu>
Date:   Sat Jul 2 13:59:10 2011 +0200

    logproto: fixed an inbalanced get_state()/put_state() pair
    
