Date:   Thu Jan 22 20:55:00 2009 +0100

    cygwin packaging updates
    
    	These patches update the cygwin packaging files. Contributed by
    	Corinna Vinschen.

commit ac991448a631bacaea41cf7d255dcb47113d9d8d
