commit f4eebb57da3e947bbd4002933bceec03cbfae519
Author: Balazs Scheidler <bazsi@balabit.hu>
Date:   Tue Dec 18 14:38:53 2007 +0100

    changed version number to 2.1.0 starting the GPL 2.1.0 branch

