commit 042dbb5b89bc9404e3be3c66e0bf92af4870eae1
Author: Balazs Scheidler <bazsi@bzorp.balabit>
Date:   Sat Apr 14 02:08:29 2007 +0200

    implemented the missing remove_if_older optio
    
