commit b61e0d46672bf41407172f20e2d0aca77835aee3
Author: Balazs Scheidler <bazsi@bzorp.balabit>
Date:   Sat Apr 14 02:06:48 2007 +0200

    fixed name resolution for unix domain socket peers
    
